    "Even if the current error rate of LLMs (Metz, 2023) does not justify generally prohibiting such applications on the basis of ensuring data accuracy, it does affect data subjects' rights.",
    "As with other areas of data-intensive technology application, there are problems with the enforcement of data subjects' rights in the case of generative models (Solove, 2023)."
